Flametal licensing
==================

This repository contains three distinct bodies of work:

1. Flametal additions — the native macOS port introduced in this fork
   relative to upstream DiaLight/Flame: the Metal host and bridge
   (macos/, src/gog_patch_dll/metal_bridge/), the macOS build and
   packaging scripts, and other changes authored in this fork.
   Copyright (c) 2025-2026 the Flametal contributors.
   Licensed under the MIT License (full text below).

2. Upstream Flame decompilation and patch layer, inherited from
   https://github.com/DiaLight/Flame — copyright its respective
   authors. Upstream is published without an explicit license; no
   rights beyond those granted by the upstream authors and applicable
   law are conveyed here.

3. Dungeon Keeper 2 itself remains copyright Electronic Arts. This
   project grants no rights to the game. A legally obtained copy
   (the GOG 1.7 release) is required to build or play.

